{"type": "article", "id": 18138, "title": "迷你冰箱", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-27T07:00:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 24, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702134808M5sSAEKHzOmfjtuU.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是创意公司 ThinkGeek 推出的两款迷你冰箱，以“Star Wars”中两款机器人为原型，很酷炫。这款冰箱高 11 寸，可以放进 6 瓶 12 盎司的易拉罐，都有保温和冷藏两种功能。此外，中间还可放一个可拆装的架子，而上面能拉开一个提杆。有橙色和蓝色两种，售价 70 美元，<a href=\"http://www.thinkgeek.com/product/ipsg/\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134805z8iZbvxEgOKXwqUF.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134806iY3ndgWlXUfALmvu.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134807jpHCbefB3qZXkPdG.jpg\" width=\"750\" height=\"500\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134807j7faUoHlXTNPRV0O.jpg\" width=\"628\" height=\"1020\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.62420382\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n"}